{"tid":873842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"習慣不求人又懶得尋人","createTime":"2018-10-23T17:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T19:34:21.000Z","uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1693d49f2d6c4c03f2fcb447cb4a978e6c88dd26","tid":873842,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"沒有東西想等可更安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家入嚟圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z59MNhEY7QA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz59MNhEY7QA&d=h6uZphh8S9XPyjlMgbYC8I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=daed770b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z59MNhEY7QA</a>"},{"pid":"e2da5d7db80d4907b80736d5d5645b60ad229e1f","tid":873842,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"作詞：林夕    作曲：楊淽<br />\n沒有花收的空曠日子<br />\n想散步行到哪裡我都可以<br />\n曾為一束花 等得很在意<br />\n要永別這種奢侈<br />\n<br />\n落得收起可愛樣子<br />\n再沒情緒去照顧多寫意<br />\n無謂再靠這 膚淺虛榮感<br />\n炫耀我有愛侶沒意思<br />\n<br />\n誰都不需要刻意討我歡心<br />\n同樣不打算虛應一句有心<br />\n習慣不求人 又懶得尋人<br />\n沒有東西想等可更安心<br />\n<br />\n如果所需要 不過一個抱枕<br />\n何必急於再找個擁抱替身<br />\n遇上多餘人 便更加煩人<br />\n沒有剛剛好的不怕等等<br />\n不要亂襯<br />\n<br />\n沒有花收將失去甚麼<br />\n將放下人有我也有的枷鎖<br />\n如若喜歡花 親手選擇過<br />\n夠美麗只需一朵<br />\n<br />\n沒單身很久怕甚麼<br />\n怕沒人去控制我騷擾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實這雙手 空一空亦可<br />\n無謂勉強拍到沒法拖<br />\n<br />\n誰都不需要刻意討我歡心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣不打算虛應一句有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習慣不求人 又懶得尋人<br />\n沒有東西想等可更安心<br />\n<br />\n如果所需要 不過一個抱枕<br />\n何必急於再找個擁抱替身<br />\n遇上多餘人 便更加煩人<br />\n沒有剛剛好的不怕等等<br />\n不要亂襯<br />\n<br />\n誰真可知我失去戀愛信心<br />\n如果真喜愛怎會需要決心<br />\n習慣不求人 又懶得尋人<br />\n讓我安享單身這個身份<br />\n<br />\n如今只需要一個可靠抱枕<br />\n何必急於再找個對象去憎<br />\n沒有新情人 亦懶得留神<br />\n讓我休一休息先再操心<br />\n不要硬撼"},{"pid":"a6f2f94f96fc24d8fcfbd1cd2190e8fef43e6617","tid":873842,"uid":2003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"其實自己一個更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2202065f6b0c195887c1a8fdb80036b40472399d","tid":873842,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:21:48.000Z","msg":".... 你係 selexxx!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e8c07e80a75651d1b748875a1acc14c296f8ad","tid":873842,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2202065f6b0c195887c1a8fdb80036b40472399d","tid":873842,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:21:48.000Z","msg":".... 你係 selexxx!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T19:34:21.000Z","msg":"？"}]}